data.description:
Beautiful well maintained ranch home surrounded by abundant gardens of perennial wildflowers, fruit trees and shrubs.
The house has 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths.
There is a full basement, poured cement with a sump pump and an outside entry. It has potential for additional bedrooms and a man cave.
The sunny kitchen has a bay window and a gas stove.
Outside there's a detached oversized 2 car garage and a shed with electric, perfect for a cabana or playhouse. There is a large above ground pool and an oversized deck with a canopy.
This house is in excellent condition.
There is a kerosene tank for heat and a propane tank for the kitchen stove and portable fireplace.
The large backyard is very private.
